race.comment: VESTAS (8) has been excellent in two runs back from a spell. She flew home from a mile back here fresh in the G3 Northwood Plume, again getting too far back around Moonee Valley second up. If she lands a pair closer here she'll be awfully hard to hold out. SHE'S BULLETPROOF (1) won the Northwood Plume up on speed, before struggling down the straight during Cup week. Back to Caulfield suits better and she'll take plenty of catching from up front. AVIATRESS (2) resumes off a good trial win. Her best form reads well for this and she files fresh. Wary of any support. PHOTOGRAPH (12) is going well and a hope at odds.
